In UGI, the skip check should be kept, else it will break things for things using hadoop-auth which don't use hadoop config files in their classpath (Oozie, HttpFS).

{code}
-      if (!skipRulesSetting) {
-        HadoopKerberosName.setConfiguration(conf);
-      }
+      HadoopKerberosName.setConfiguration(conf);
{code}
